Package: opitools
Type: Package
Title: A Tool for Analyzing Opinions in a Text Document
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Monsuru Adepeju [cre, aut],
Maintainer: Monsuru Adepeju <monsuur2010@yahoo.com>
Description: This tool analyzes the opinions inherent in a text document
  relating to a specific subject (A), and assesses
  the impacts that opinion expressed with respect to another subject (B) 
  have on subject A. This package is specifically designed for application 
  to social media datasets, such as Twitter.
Language: en-US
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/MAnalytics/opitools
BugReports: https://github.com/MAnalytics/opitools/issues/1
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
